n<br />\n可能比左好多錢上級,先有得派去澳門</blockquote><br />\n呢個試吓光復行動落去搞事<br />\n俾人打撚死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即刻拉返佢企後排, 同D女仔企一齊啦"},{"pid":"f61d1d8f8f448e9c3f12ca8e85aacaef913b29e7","tid":373963,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現場有幾臭有幾焗大家都唔清楚。有啲巴打仲話自己大隻過解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠唔夠膽同解放軍鬥跑山鬥刻苦？咁都有得拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5157483e7ac71330ea09385b1fdde7ea9b12b2b","tid":373963,"uid":126256,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現場有幾臭有幾焗大家都唔清楚。有啲巴打仲話自己大隻過解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠唔夠膽同解放軍鬥跑山鬥刻苦？咁都有得拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知唔知陳忠和點訓練女排<br />\n一樣係跑山<br />\n結果咪全部傷晒膝頭哥囉<br />\n人地就科學訓練盡量唔整傷人<br />\n你就跑山當體能訓練<br />\n醫療又跟唔上<br />\n咪全部傷兵同人鬥囉"},{"pid":"848087b5dd594a56d13acd9284a3c0b0d905d35d","tid":373963,"uid":35993,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現場有幾臭有幾焗大家都唔清楚。有啲巴打仲話自己大隻過解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠唔夠膽同解放軍鬥跑山鬥刻苦？咁都有得拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔見澳門啲消防暈？唔洗跑山鬥刻苦啦，呢排旺角咁多樓要拆，去倒返日泥頭咪知有冇料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa6853ea0f9a21d0ebcf45f5f4c3c5b1c6a56b7","tid":373963,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:47:51.000Z","msg":"最後咪又賣溫馨熱血，澳門過一個星期又無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7edda9a7634854f9adadd7d4368b0a4d8f1059","tid":373963,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:31:38.000Z","msg":"駐澳白雪雪排骨兵心諗：<br />\n我比咁多錢派去澳門係當渡假，你老母崔世安仲乜擺我地上枱？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791068/xlarge/c596d277442e7e12b724816906740b9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791068%2Fxlarge%2Fc596d277442e7e12b724816906740b9e.jpg&h=f4987a03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed672d0ff84875a7ed87507e1a7eb31ac9e2679e","tid":373963,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"返北京啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cb1b4fe3603512704b074481bf10cb4a4dcefc","tid":373963,"uid":26721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fce0fd7f1f9c1ec11d201868f2b013dbad0834","tid":373963,"uid":30857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"露哂底 成堆排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cda8a8625e3a6ccb227dd440393a594bc07128","tid":373963,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"臨危時求求上天庇佑啊!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce22f28555563bde26996bbd4ab4f4af508fffa","tid":373963,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/